Ogres in the Sands
The ogres from the Sands have joined forces with our enemies! Help the Shei-Var clan by killing the three ogres. Rivar also wants you to search the Ogres' treasures for useful items!
#subobj  1
Find the first of the three ogres, kill him and plunder his chest!
Find and finish the first of the three ogres. Also he might have a treasure.
#subobj  2
Find the second of the three ogres, kill him and plunder his chest!
Also find and kill the second of the three ogres. Loot the ogre's treasure.
#subobj  3
Find the third of the three ogres, kill him and plunder his chest!
Track down the third of the three ogres and eliminate him. See what the ogre has hidden in his chest.

